The travelling caravan will include international tax consultants, immigration lawyers, accountants, marketeers and merchandising specialists. The Rolling Stones 'brand’ is effectively several different companies, variously incorporated in tax-friendly domiciles. Each company is responsible for a different aspect of the Stones’ operations – touring, record sales, merchandising, copyright, video and internet marketing.
